  case $(menu "Install" "ŅĮ▓  Package\n’ē©  Web App\n’Æē  TUI\n’Æć  Service\n’é¼  Browser\nŅŁŁ  Utility\nŅ»Å  Style\n¾░Ą«  Development\n’ģ£  Editor\n’Æē  Terminal\n¾▒Üż  AI\n’äø  Gaming") in
