  case $(menu "Install" "’Æć  1password\n’Æć  Bitwarden\n’ć┐  Discord\nŅ£ć  Dropbox\n’ŹČ  LibreOffice\n’Æć  LocalSend\n’Æć  ObsStudio\n’Æć  Obsidian\n’Æć  Signal\n’å╝  Spotify\n’Æć  Typora\n’Æć  Tailscale\n’Æć  Zoom") in
